- NEMA 17 Stepper Motor and Stepper Driver (Pololu A4988 works well)

- 2-56x3/8” screws for mounting T-ring and tripod washer
- M3 screws for mounting lidar to lidar stand

- USB mini cable -- cut in half and rewire to either side of slip ring
